chore(frontend): drop redundant _redirects in favour of wrangler SPA config

Workers Static Assets handles SPA fallback natively via the wrangler.toml
`assets.not_found_handling = "single-page-application"` directive, so the
legacy Pages-style `/* /index.html 200` rule is no longer needed. The new
Cloudflare validator also rejects it as a potential infinite loop, which
blocked the most recent deploy.
